00:29:21.874 --> 00:29:24.536
I know.
It's my greatest fear.

269
00:29:24.577 --> 00:29:28.013
You know. he is so cute.

270
00:29:28.047 --> 00:29:30.174
- I wonder where he works out?
- Save it. Deb.

271
00:29:30.216 --> 00:29:32.810
I mean. there is life after exercise.

272
00:29:32.852 --> 00:29:33.978
One of these days...

273
00:29:34.020 --> 00:29:36.318
I'm gonna set you up with a real guy...

274
00:29:36.355 --> 00:29:38.346
teach you to get your priorities straight.

275
00:29:38.391 --> 00:29:39.756
I think Sheila's more interested...

276
00:29:39.792 --> 00:29:41.919
in dissecting bodies than their outsides.

277
00:29:41.961 --> 00:29:42.913
Give her time.

278
00:29:42.939 --> 00:29:45.362
Her hormones will kick in some day.

279
00:29:45.398 --> 00:29:49.356
Deb. later in life. you'll appreciate my motto.

280
00:29:49.401 --> 00:29:50.692
What's that?

281
00:29:50.718 --> 00:29:53.192
Mind over matter.

282
00:29:54.539 --> 00:29:55.699
I'll see you later. OK?

283
00:30:02.581 --> 00:30:04.173
Alice. can you leave here?

284
00:30:04.216 --> 00:30:05.444
What's wrong?

285
00:30:05.484 --> 00:30:07.315
Kincaid and Joey died last night.

286
00:30:07.352 --> 00:30:08.910
What?

287
00:30:08.954 --> 00:30:11.354
Hey. Rick. come here!

288
00:30:11.389 --> 00:30:12.549
Stay with her.

289
00:30:13.558 --> 00:30:15.457
Kristen. what happened?

290
00:30:16.460 --> 00:30:18.655
Look. you're gonna hear all kinds of stories.

291
00:30:19.897 --> 00:30:22.161
And after all we've been through together...

292
00:30:22.833 --> 00:30:24.926
how could I let him get to them?

293
00:30:24.969 --> 00:30:26.698
We were a team.

294
00:30:27.404 --> 00:30:29.565
I'm gonna get that son of a bitch.

295
00:30:29.607 --> 00:30:30.767
Who?

296
00:30:31.842 --> 00:30:33.537
Rick. we gotta go.

297
00:30:34.478 --> 00:30:35.877
- Now.
- I'm coming.

298
00:30:36.747 --> 00:30:38.374
Before it's too late.

299
00:30:38.415 --> 00:30:40.474
I gotta go.
I guess I'll talk to you later.

