320
00:30:56.199 --> 00:30:57.928
So. why the haunted house?

321
00:30:59.035 --> 00:31:01.162
It's not just a house.

322
00:31:01.204 --> 00:31:03.502
It's his home.

323
00:31:03.540 --> 00:31:05.838
He's waiting in there for me to dream.

324
00:31:05.875 --> 00:31:06.533
Hey. it's OK.

325
00:31:06.559 --> 00:31:07.367
We're with you.

326
00:31:08.311 --> 00:31:10.107
I told you. you can't help me.

327
00:31:10.979 --> 00:31:12.708
This isn't a normal nightmare.

328
00:31:13.782 --> 00:31:15.079
I'm history.

329
00:31:16.185 --> 00:31:17.777
I don't get it.

330
00:31:19.855 --> 00:31:21.379
- Come on.
- Jeez. What'd I miss?

331
00:31:22.224 --> 00:31:24.055
She told us a story about Freddy.

332
00:31:24.092 --> 00:31:26.788
Fred Krueger.
He's a town legend.

333
00:31:26.828 --> 00:31:29.319
He was a child killer freed on a technicality.

334
00:31:30.332 --> 00:31:31.458
So?

335
00:31:31.500 --> 00:31:33.764
So. a lot of parents got pissed off...

336
00:31:34.703 --> 00:31:36.932
and. according to Kris...

337
00:31:36.971 --> 00:31:38.598
they hunted him down and roasted him...

338
00:31:38.639 --> 00:31:40.334
like a Thanksgiving turkey.

339
00:31:41.309 --> 00:31:42.469
Nice neighborhood.

340
00:31:43.544 --> 00:31:45.273
Anyway. that's where it gets weird.

341
00:31:45.313 --> 00:31:48.214
She says that he comes back in dreams.

342
00:31:48.249 --> 00:31:49.944
And if he kills you in your dream...

343
00:31:50.985 --> 00:31:52.384
you're dead for real.

344
00:31:56.224 --> 00:31:58.317
Now I lay me down to sleep.

345
00:31:58.359 --> 00:32:01.351
The master of dreams. my soul I'll keep.

346
00:32:02.430 --> 00:32:05.159
Dream master.
I think I remember the rhyme.

347
00:32:09.002 --> 00:32:11.971
Kristen. get the hell away from that house!

348
00:32:12.005 --> 00:32:13.472
�Andale!

349
00:32:18.578 --> 00:32:20.603
You don't have to go if you don't want to.

350
00:32:20.647 --> 00:32:21.807
I'll take care of you.

351
00:32:24.317 --> 00:32:25.477
I better go.

352
00:32:25.518 --> 00:32:27.042
OK...

353
00:32:27.087 --> 00:32:29.282
but I'll call you tonight. and we'll get through this.

