01:01:13.179 --> 01:01:15.409
All the towns in America...

688
01:01:15.448 --> 01:01:17.916
and I gotta move to the Bermuda Triangle.

689
01:01:19.286 --> 01:01:20.583
That's great.

690
01:03:07.423 --> 01:03:09.391
See ya. Alvin.

691
01:03:09.425 --> 01:03:11.052
Hey. he ain't no paper man.

692
01:03:11.093 --> 01:03:12.072
Why. don't you know him?

693
01:03:12.098 --> 01:03:13.254
That's "Hot Fingers" Curly.

694
01:03:13.295 --> 01:03:15.695
Boy. he really swings out hoppin' with a jive.

695
01:03:15.731 --> 01:03:17.995
- You want to dance?
- Do I?

696
01:05:59.923 --> 01:06:01.151
What'll it be?

697
01:06:05.662 --> 01:06:06.672
Come on. honey.

698
01:06:06.698 --> 01:06:08.986
I don't want to be here forever.

699
01:06:13.669 --> 01:06:17.469
If the food don't kill ya. the service will.

700
01:06:17.506 --> 01:06:19.599
Help us. Alice!

701
01:06:21.977 --> 01:06:23.877
The usual.

702
01:06:23.912 --> 01:06:25.971
No. Alice. don't let him do it!

703
01:06:26.014 --> 01:06:27.572
My favorite.

704
01:06:27.616 --> 01:06:29.083
No! Come on. no!

705
01:06:29.117 --> 01:06:30.516
Eeney. meeney. miney...

706
01:06:30.552 --> 01:06:32.110
Come on. no!

707
01:06:32.154 --> 01:06:33.314
Moe!

708
01:06:36.224 --> 01:06:37.816
No. Alice. don't let him do it!

709
01:06:37.858 --> 01:06:40.326
Rick. you little meatball.

710
01:06:40.361 --> 01:06:41.726
I love soul food.

711
01:06:41.762 --> 01:06:44.731
No! No! Stop!

712
01:06:53.007 --> 01:06:54.770
Bring me more.

713
01:07:02.850 --> 01:07:05.613
Your shift is over.

714
01:07:39.218 --> 01:07:40.617
Come on. We have to hurry!

715
01:07:40.653 --> 01:07:42.712
- What's going on?
- I'm driving.

716
01:07:51.764 --> 01:07:52.972
He's going after Debbie.

717
01:07:52.998 --> 01:07:54.130
I've got to stop him.

718
01:07:54.166 --> 01:07:54.837
We got to stop him.

719
01:07:54.863 --> 01:07:55.861
I'm with you on this thing.

720
01:07:55.901 --> 01:07:57.392
I want to help you.

721
01:07:57.418 --> 01:07:59.224
I'm on your side. OK?

722
01:08:15.453 --> 01:08:16.818
Here we are.

723
01:08:25.429 --> 01:08:27.420
Come on. We have to hurry!

724
01:08:27.464 --> 01:08:29.659
- What's going on?
- I'm driving.

725
01:08:46.983 --> 01:08:48.780
I don't believe in you.

726
01:08:48.819 --> 01:08:50.979
I believe in you.

727
01:09:03.766 --> 01:09:06.633
No pain... no gain.

728
01:09:12.675 --> 01:09:14.441
He's going after Debbie.

729
01:09:14.467 --> 01:09:16.158
I've got to stop him.

730
01:09:41.703 --> 01:09:45.968
Help me!

731
01:09:54.915 --> 01:09:56.314
Here we are.

732
01:10:03.390 --> 01:10:04.721
Come on. We have to hurry!

733
01:10:04.758 --> 01:10:05.620
What's going on?

734
01:10:05.646 --> 01:10:06.614
I'm driving.

735
01:10:13.633 --> 01:10:14.754
He's going after Debbie.

736
01:10:14.780 --> 01:10:15.828
I've got to stop him.

737
01:10:15.868 --> 01:10:18.701
I get the weirdest feeling
we've done this before.

738
01:11:01.446 --> 01:11:03.176
Come on.
We have to hurry.

739
01:11:03.202 --> 01:11:04.108
I'm driving.

740
01:11:04.149 --> 01:11:06.912
Oh. my God.

741
01:11:06.951 --> 01:11:08.418
We're both asleep.

742
01:11:08.452 --> 01:11:10.716
He's got us going in circles.

743
01:11:10.754 --> 01:11:12.688
We got to go!

744
01:11:31.308 --> 01:11:35.676
You can check in. but you can't check out.

745
01:11:42.218 --> 01:11:44.209
What the hell was that?

746
01:11:46.523 --> 01:11:48.047
She's gone.

747
01:11:49.559 --> 01:11:52.824
I've collected her like the others.

748
01:12:03.038 --> 01:12:05.529
All right. I'm gonna punch his ticket in.

749
01:12:41.709 --> 01:12:43.506
I'm sorry.

750
01:12:43.678 --> 01:12:45.111
All right. get him in there.

751
01:12:53.253 --> 01:12:55.084
Base. this is med seven.

752
01:12:55.121 --> 01:12:59.854
We have a male Caucasian. 16-18 years of age.

753
01:12:59.893 --> 01:13:03.021
Multiple lacerations about the head and neck area.

754
01:13:03.063 --> 01:13:05.361
Possible internal injuries.

755
01:13:05.398 --> 01:13:06.259
What's that do?

756
01:13:06.285 --> 01:13:07.923
Relaxes your boyfriend.

757
01:13:07.968 --> 01:13:09.283
Put the needle down.

758
01:13:09.309 --> 01:13:10.664
Rules is rules.

759
01:13:10.704 --> 01:13:12.535
He stays awake!

760
01:13:12.572 --> 01:13:14.631
Those are my rules. understand?

761
01:13:14.674 --> 01:13:16.039
Are you nuts?

762
01:13:16.076 --> 01:13:17.805
He's allergic. OK?

763
01:13:17.844 --> 01:13:20.869
You should have said something in the first place.

764
01:13:20.913 --> 01:13:22.346
Damn kids.

765
01:13:23.549 --> 01:13:25.779
Don't let them put you to sleep.

766
01:13:25.818 --> 01:13:28.787
We have to get ready for him.

767
01:13:44.737 --> 01:13:46.327
When does he have surgery?

768
01:13:46.353 --> 01:13:47.671
Fifteen minutes.

769
01:13:47.705 --> 01:13:49.138
Let him be. Alice!

770
01:13:51.409 --> 01:13:52.967
They're gonna kill him!

771
01:13:53.011 --> 01:13:54.842
What are you talking about?

772
01:13:54.879 --> 01:13:56.005
Let me go!

773
01:13:56.047 --> 01:13:57.145
Alice!
Damn it!

774
01:13:57.171 --> 01:13:58.267
Get back here!

775
01:14:32.916 --> 01:14:34.213
Come on!

776
01:15:19.360 --> 01:15:20.987
No. No gas.

777
01:15:21.029 --> 01:15:23.497
No gas. No. Don't put...

778
01:16:48.280 --> 01:16:50.111
Fuckin' "A."

779
01:17:00.925 --> 01:17:03.860
Well. it ain't Dr. Seuss.

780
01:17:10.467 --> 01:17:13.436
Get away from him. you son of a bitch!

781
01:17:25.715 --> 01:17:27.342
- I saw him. He was here.
- I know.

782
01:17:27.383 --> 01:17:29.647
We have to get out of this place.

783
01:17:56.845 --> 01:17:59.905
Out for a spin. lovebirds?

784
01:17:59.948 --> 01:18:01.347
Dan. hold on!

785
01:18:26.974 --> 01:18:30.171
Alice. it's too late.

786
01:18:31.545 --> 01:18:32.671
He's hemorrhaging.

787
01:18:32.713 --> 01:18:34.874
Bring him out of it!
 Hurry!

788
01:18:48.795 --> 01:18:51.127
You got to put me back under now!

789
01:18:51.164 --> 01:18:54.429
Relax. son.
 It was rough. but we pulled you out.

790
01:18:54.467 --> 01:18:56.059
You're gonna be OK.

791
01:18:57.337 --> 01:19:02.104
One. two. Freddy's coming for you

792
01:19:02.142 --> 01:19:06.670
Three. four. better lock your door

793
01:19:06.713 --> 01:19:11.046
Five. six. grab your crucifix

794
01:19:11.083 --> 01:19:13.244
Seven. eight. better stay up late

795
01:19:15.688 --> 01:19:20.091
Nine. ten. never sleep again

796
01:19:20.125 --> 01:19:22.992
Welcome to Wonderland. Alice.

797
01:20:18.849 --> 01:20:20.448
You've got their power.

798
01:20:20.474 --> 01:20:22.046
I've got their souls.

799
01:20:22.085 --> 01:20:23.279
Come on.

800
01:20:45.074 --> 01:20:47.133
Banzai.

801
01:21:01.856 --> 01:21:05.019
You think you've got what it takes?

802
01:21:06.594 --> 01:21:11.588
I've been guarding my gate for a long time. bitch.

803
01:22:10.723 --> 01:22:15.524
I am eternal.

804
01:22:29.508 --> 01:22:33.968
Now I lay me down to sleep.

805
01:22:34.012 --> 01:22:40.144
The master of dreams. my soul I'll keep.

806
01:22:40.185 --> 01:22:44.713
In the reflection of my mind's eye...

807
01:22:44.756 --> 01:22:49.419
Evil will see itself. and it shall die!

808
01:23:11.048 --> 01:23:12.947
Let them out!

809
01:23:31.301 --> 01:23:33.166
You're dead. Krueger.

810
01:24:44.804 --> 01:24:46.635
Thank you. Alice.

811
01:24:46.673 --> 01:24:48.334
You saved us.

812
01:24:49.442 --> 01:24:51.637
Freedom.

813
01:25:06.125 --> 01:25:08.218
Rest in hell.

814
01:26:00.077 --> 01:26:02.375
You know. I slept through all of last night...

815
01:26:02.412 --> 01:26:04.380
and I haven't done that in days.

816
01:26:04.414 --> 01:26:06.780
I'm still having trouble.

817
01:26:06.817 --> 01:26:10.617
I can sleep two. maybe three hours. if I'm lucky.

818
01:26:10.654 --> 01:26:11.951
I don't mind. though.

819
01:26:11.988 --> 01:26:14.548
I have more reasons to stay awake now.

820
01:26:17.027 --> 01:26:18.187
Come on.

821
01:26:19.663 --> 01:26:20.788
Make a wish.

822
01:26:20.830 --> 01:26:23.924
Come on. you don't believe in that stuff.

823
01:26:23.966 --> 01:26:27.561
Yeah. I do. and I think you do. too.

824
01:26:29.505 --> 01:26:30.665
Here it goes.

825
01:26:40.416 --> 01:26:41.644
What'd you wish for?

826
01:26:50.825 --> 01:26:53.453
If I tell you. it won't come true.

